-- Arkema Says Second-Quarter Sales, Ebitda to Increase Versus First Quarter
-- David Whitehouse
-- 2010-07-01T06:04:27Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-01/arkema-says-second-quarter-sales-ebitda-to-increase-versus-first-quarter.html

          
          
             Arkema SA said that sales and
earnings before interest, taxes, depreciation and amortization
will increase significantly in the second quarter versus the
first, helped by an improved economic environment.  
 The news came in a Business Wire statement.  
          
          


  


        